13	# PasswordInput
14	
15	A password input field that extends the standard TextField with a visibility toggle button.
16	By default the input displays masked text (`type="password"`); clicking the toggle reveals
17	the plain text (`type="text"`). This component wraps a single `<input>` and adds the
18	toggle affordance without duplicating TextField's form-participation logic.
