163	
164	> **Callback props (`on_submit`, `on_clear`)**: These are provided by the adapter layer, not the core state machine. The adapter MUST wire: `on_submit` fires when `Event::Submit` is processed (Enter key or SubmitTrigger click), receiving the current `ctx.value`; `on_clear` fires when `Event::Clear` is processed (ClearTrigger click or Escape key).
165	
166	### 1.5 Debounce Timer Integration
167	
168	The debounce timer is a `PendingEffect` managed by the state machine, not a simple adapter-side `setTimeout`. This ensures the timer lifecycle is tied to the machine's effect system and properly cleaned up on unmount or state changes.
169	
170	- **On `Event::Change`**: The machine cancels any existing debounce timer effect and starts a new one with the configured `debounce_ms` duration.
171	- **On timer expiration**: The effect fires `Event::DebounceExpired`, which triggers the `on_change` callback with the current `ctx.value`.
172	- **Rapid inputs**: Each new `Event::Change` resets the timer, ensuring only the final value after the user stops typing triggers the callback.
173	- **`Event::Submit`**: Cancels any pending debounce timer and fires the callback immediately (explicit submit should not be delayed).
174	- **`Event::Clear`**: Cancels any pending debounce timer and fires the callback immediately with an empty string.
175	
176	**Props change (`debounce_ms` mutation)**: When the `debounce_ms` prop changes while a debounce timer is active, the machine cancels the active timer and starts a fresh one with the new duration. A `debounce_ms` value of `Some(0)` is treated as `Some(1)` to prevent microtask-level race conditions.
177	
178	### 1.6 Full Machine Implementation
179	
180	```rust
181	/// The machine for the SearchInput component.
182	pub struct Machine;
183	
184	impl ars_core::Machine for Machine {
185	    type State = State;
186	    type Event = Event;
187	    type Context = Context;
188	    type Props = Props;
189	    type Api<'a> = Api<'a>;
190	    type Messages = Messages;
191	
192	    fn init(props: &Self::Props, env: &Env, messages: &Self::Messages) -> (Self::State, Self::Context) {
193	        let locale = env.locale.clone();
194	        let messages = messages.clone();
195	        let state = State::Idle;
196	        let ctx = Context {
197	            value: match &props.value {
198	                Some(v) => Bindable::controlled(v.clone()),
199	                None => Bindable::uncontrolled(props.default_value.clone()),
200	            },
201	            disabled: props.disabled,
202	            readonly: props.readonly,
203	            invalid: props.invalid,
204	            focused: false,
205	            focus_visible: false,
206	            loading: false,
207	            name: props.name.clone(),
208	            placeholder: props.placeholder.clone(),
209	            is_composing: false,
210	            has_description: false,
211	            locale,
212	            messages,
213	            ids: ComponentIds::from_id(&props.id),
214	        };
215	        (state, ctx)
216	    }
217	
218	    fn transition(
219	        state: &Self::State,
220	        event: &Self::Event,
221	        ctx: &Self::Context,
222	        _props: &Self::Props,
223	    ) -> Option<TransitionPlan<Self>> {
224	        match event {
225	            Event::Focus { is_keyboard } => {
226	                let is_kb = *is_keyboard;
227	                Some(TransitionPlan::to(State::Focused).apply(move |ctx| {
228	                    ctx.focused = true;
229	                    ctx.focus_visible = is_kb;
230	                }))
231	            }
232	            Event::Blur => {
233	                let is_loading = ctx.loading;
234	                Some(TransitionPlan::to(if is_loading { State::Searching } else { State::Idle })
235	                    .apply(|ctx| {
236	                        ctx.focused = false;
237	                        ctx.focus_visible = false;
238	                    }))
239	            }
240	            Event::Change(val) => {
241	                if ctx.disabled || ctx.readonly { return None; }
242	                let val = val.clone();
243	                Some(TransitionPlan::context_only(move |ctx| {
244	                    ctx.value.set(val);
245	                }))
246	            }
247	            Event::Clear => {
248	                if ctx.disabled || ctx.readonly { return None; }
249	                Some(TransitionPlan::context_only(|ctx| {
250	                    ctx.value.set(String::new());
251	                }))
252	            }
253	            Event::Submit => {
254	                if ctx.disabled { return None; }
255	                Some(TransitionPlan::to(State::Searching).apply(|ctx| {
256	                    ctx.loading = true;
257	                }))
258	            }
259	            Event::SetSearching(loading) => {
260	                let loading = *loading;
261	                let is_focused = ctx.focused;
262	                if !loading {
263	                    Some(TransitionPlan::to(if is_focused { State::Focused } else { State::Idle })
264	                        .apply(move |ctx| { ctx.loading = loading; }))
265	                } else {
266	                    Some(TransitionPlan::to(State::Searching)
267	                        .apply(move |ctx| { ctx.loading = loading; }))
268	                }
269	            }
270	            Event::CompositionStart => {
271	                Some(TransitionPlan::context_only(|ctx| { ctx.is_composing = true; }))
272	            }
273	            Event::CompositionEnd => {
274	                Some(TransitionPlan::context_only(|ctx| { ctx.is_composing = false; }))
275	            }
276	            Event::DebounceExpired | Event::CancelDebounce => {
277	                // Handled by the effect system; no state/context change
278	                None
279	            }
280	        }
281	    }
282	
283	    fn connect<'a>(
284	        state: &'a Self::State,
285	        ctx: &'a Self::Context,
286	        props: &'a Self::Props,
287	        send: &'a dyn Fn(Self::Event),
288	    ) -> Self::Api<'a> {
289	        Api { state, ctx, props, send }
290	    }
291	}
292	```
